haracterId":13}],"windowDisplayName":"하구미","body":"응, 상점가 사람들도 그래서\n바로 구급차를 불러서 병원에서 수술을 받기로 했어.\n……그런데……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":13,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":13,"voiceId":"band3-012-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":13}],"windowDisplayName":"하구미","body":"어라. 엄마한테 문자가 왔네?\n무슨 일이지. 웬일로……\n…………","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":13,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":13,"voiceId":"band3-012-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":13}],"windowDisplayName":"하구미","body":"미……미안, 또 지각했네……!\n허억……허억, 허억.\n……헉……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":13,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":13,"voiceId":"band3-012-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":13}],"windowDisplayName":"하구미","body":"그, 그래……팀은 별문제 없지만\n잠깐……병원에 갔……\n……아무튼 괜찮아! 자 밴드 하자.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":13,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":13,"voiceId":"band3-012-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"charac